      <scopecontent id="aspace_d5a057f23a0836e14ad4019b406edca3">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs of Yale and New Haven. Included in the collection are building, sports, circus, and beach scenes. Many of these photographs were used in This Was Connecticut: Images of a Vanished World (1977).</p>  
